    "description": "一只可爱的羊驼满怀期待地来到了一个名叫窝窝岛的神秘地方。在这个如梦如幻的岛屿上，它即将开启一场充满惊喜的休闲快乐冒险之旅。岛上不仅有美不胜收的风景，湛蓝的天空下是碧绿的草地，五彩斑斓的花朵争奇斗艳，清澈的溪流潺潺流淌。还有众多神奇的武器，散发着神秘光芒的宝剑、拥有强大魔力的法杖。更有凶猛的怪兽，张牙舞爪，吼声震天。但勇敢的羊驼毫不畏惧，它眼中闪烁着坚定的光芒，兴奋地踏上了这场未知的冒险征程，准备迎接一切挑战，去探索岛屿深处的秘密，书写属于自己的传奇故事。<br><strong>游戏里还有地牢，迷宫，BOSS ，秘密地点等</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136260/extras/a2088b01a5f70e823da21c16f1472462.avif?t=1724138765\" width=500 height=350 /></span><br><strong>这是一款开放世界的游戏，你可以自由自在的游玩，可以升级，冒险，解密，还有许多秘密的地方。</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136260/extras/7faadc8fb5054f41860a70e4af916159.avif?t=1724138765\" width=400 height=533 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136260/extras/f519b59167f4bb5da5b8859782360c3c.avif?t=1724138765\" width=500 height=374 /></span><br><strong>游戏武器还有装备效果，右键会有技能效果。</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136260/extras/9fd2a2cc6e60c39a235be3b9091a9508.avif?t=1724138765\" width=500 height=346 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136260/extras/fc5eaf77b23b6ecfaf1c3827f98251fc.avif?t=1724138765\" width=500 height=360 /></span>、<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136260/extras/86678630a944bee73dbacb596471a258.avif?t=1724138765\" width=500 height=328 /></span><br><strong>武器在世界不同的地方，需要自己的探索，但是他们都有等级限制，所以你需要升级才能拿取。</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136260/extras/75f71a703a81c868bbf777582110c284.avif?t=1724138765\" width=500 height=312 /></span><br><strong>休息的时候看看风景听听海风~</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136260/extras/2657fd134ee51bb560c6be61e1ce6c8d.avif?t=1724138765\" width=500 height=300 /></span>",
